4, 94.2269, 93.3706, 95.493, 95.572, 95.4994, 95.6967, 96.529, 97.0748, 96.4356, 95.4786, 95.4778, 95.5407, 95.8724, 95.6712, 97.1589, 96.5786, 97.3491, 98.3256, 98.558, 97.5775, 97.5109, 98.9696, 99.1359, 98.7519, 98.0237, 96.3647, 95.2612, 95.6097, 96.8845, 96.4946, 98.1867, 99.1785, 97.9103, 97.9031, 98.4216, 100.0012, 104.1824, 104.0674, 105.9974, 106.787, 108.2743, 107.571, 106.6582, 106.7364, 105.9942, 107.005, 107.4217, 106.092, 106.7268, 107.2377, 108.3925, 106.6797, 107.8336, 108.7562, 108.4161, 110.0595, 110.201, 109.8037, 110.5845, 109.5956, 110.3908, 110.9221, 108.6153, 111.2666, 110.3419, 111.7611, 111.0452, 111.8077, 112.4662, 110.7765, 109.9838, 108.4383, 106.0869, 105.1456, 104.3789, 103.8959, 104.8706, 106.0857, 108.1726, 107.6791, 110.1552, 109.3079, 110.7075, 111.6397, 109.8772, 110.0932, 110.4619, 110.636, 111.9915, 110.1267, 110.2671, 108.3449, 108.6876, 106.6259, 107.0457, 106.1306, 104.9491, 105.1121, 103.6916, 103.5484, 103.764, 102.9896, 101.666, 102.4101, 102.5117, 104.2531, 104.1695, 104.3164, 104.5474, 104.2273, 102.5719, 99.4839, 98.6447, 98.4679, 96.5428, 95.2011, 95.368, 97.3126, 95.2759, 95.4242, 95.4473, 95.5574, 94.3923, 93.4879, 91.7472, 91.194, 90.3863, 89.8646, 87.7585, 88.6852, 88.8114, 88.8832, 89.0085, 89.7632, 88.762, 88.1358, 85.5591, 85.9885, 85.2247, 85.4255, 84.8405, 87.4456, 86.5844, 89.5726, 91.0777, 89.7488, 89.5602, 90.2768, 89.9277, 91.5333, 90.365, 90.3759, 90.6564, 90.5363], "summary_html": "<h1>持仓博弈异常信号 (dH Bollinger Breakout) -- 通过 (Sharpe 0.99)</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>该策略利用期货交易所每日公布的前20大会员多空持仓数据，构造 dH 指标衡量市场主力参与者的多空力量对比。当 dH 值突破其布林通道（N日均值 +/- w倍标准差）时，认为持仓结构出现异常，发出方向性交易信号。策略的核心假设是：当市场主力参与者（套保商、信息优势者）在某一方向上大幅增仓时，会导致 dH 出现极端值，预示短期内价格将向该方向运动。该信号本质上是一种基本面/持仓结构因子，与传统量价趋势信号低相关。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.74</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>2.8%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>3.8%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-7.1%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.05</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>1759</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>0.92</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>-0.46</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.2 / 0.68</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>0.79</td><td>1.56</td><td>0.94</td><td>1.4</td><td>0.51</td><td>0.45</td><td>0.88</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-3.92</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>memberdiff20</code></td><td>席位净持仓差</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每日</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>57</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>1758</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>94.1%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>47.9</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p><strong>dH 指标（差值版，Report 1）</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">dH_t^{diff} = lH_t - sH_t</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">lH_t</span> 为 t 日前20大会员多头总持仓量，<span class=\"math-tex\">sH_t</span> 为 t 日前20大会员空头总持仓量。数据字段：<code>memberdiff20</code>。</p>\n<p><strong>dH 指标（比值版，Report 2）</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">dH_t^{ratio} = \\frac{lH_t}{sH_t}</div>\n<p>比值版减少了合约换月时的跳跃（跳跃幅度从 539.65% 降至 6.22%）。数据字段：<code>member_all</code>。</p>\n<p><strong>布林通道信号</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">MA_N(t) = \\frac{1}{N}\\sum_{i=0}^{N-1} dH_{t-i}</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">upper(t) = MA_N(t) + w \\cdot \\sigma_N(t), \\quad lower(t) = MA_N(t) - w \\cdot \\sigma_N(t)</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">signal_t = \\begin{cases} +1 &amp; dH_t &gt; upper(t) \\\\ -1 &amp; dH_t &lt; lower(t) \\\\ signal_{t-1} &amp; \\text{otherwise (持续方向)} \\end{cases}</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">N</span> 为移动平均窗口，<span class=\"math-tex\">w</span> 为通道宽度倍数，<span class=\"math-tex\">\\sigma_N</span> 为 N 日滚动标准差。</p>\n<h2>迭代记录</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>诊断</th><th>行动</th><th>效果</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>Sharpe 0.46, 换手率 2.74, 信号前半段强后半段弱</td><td>初始实现：diff+ratio两种dH, 4个参数组合, hold=5</td><td>diff_N60_w1.0 最优 (0.46)，ratio版全部负Sharpe</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>换手率过高吃掉收益；ratio版无效</td><td>增加hold_days到10减少换手；扩展diff参数网格(N=40-100, w=0.8-1.2)；增加IC gate变体</td><td><strong>Sharpe 0.46 -&gt; 0.985</strong> (关键转折)。换手率1.72。diff_N80_w1.2最优</td></tr><tr><td>R3</td><td>所有gate通过，继续优化</td><td>增加_cs/_ts归一化；N=100-120+w=1.5参数探索；hold=15变体</td><td>Sharpe维持0.985，多个变体&gt;0.87，策略稳健</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>关键转折</strong>: R1-&gt;R2 的 Sharpe 翻倍(0.46-&gt;0.99)来自两个改进：(1) hold_days 5-&gt;10 大幅降低换手成本；(2) 更大的N(80)和w(1.2)让通道信号更稳定，减少噪声交易。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>数据字段</strong>: <code>memberdiff20</code>（前20大会员多空持仓差值），非空率约 23%</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全商品期货（64个品种，覆盖率受 memberdiff20 非空率限制）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 持续方向 + 10天再平衡</li>\n<li><strong>与因子库相关性</strong>: max_corr=0.43 (vs tianfeng_lsr)，判定为 marginal，非冗余</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - 比值版(member_all)在商品期货上效果差（Sharpe&lt;0.5），差值版明显优于比值版\n<p>- 信号依赖 memberdiff20 字段非空，部分品种/年份数据缺失 - 截面IC接近零(0.004)，信号主要是时序性质而非截面排名</p>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.24s</li>\n</ul>"}